def region_function(country):
    if country in ['Australia', 'Japan', 'Korea', 'United States']:
        return "Pacific"
    
    if country in [ 'Canada', 'USA', 'Mexico', "Brazil", "Chile"]:
        return "America"
    
    return "Europe"

mouse_selection1 = alt.selection(type='multi', fields=['country'], on='mouseover', nearest=True)

year_slider = alt.binding_range(min=2015, max=2020, step=1)
slider_selection1 = alt.selection_single(bind=year_slider, fields=['year'], name="select", init = {"year":2020})


def make_plot(df, X_name, Y_name, val_type, title_name, mouse_selection, slider_selection):
    
    logscale = False
    
    filter1 = df["variable"] == val_type
    df = df.loc[filter1].copy()
    
    
    X_name = alt.X(X_name, scale=alt.Scale(domain=[0, df[X_name].max()]))
    Y_name = alt.Y(Y_name, scale=alt.Scale(domain=[0, df[Y_name].max()]))
    
    if logscale:
        Y_name = Y_name +":Q"
        Y_name = alt.Y(Y_name, scale=alt.Scale(type='log'))
        X_name = X_name +":Q"
        X_name = alt.X(X_name, scale=alt.Scale(type='log'))    
    
    base =  alt.Chart(df).properties(width=320, height=280, title = title_name)#.transform_filter(
#        alt.FieldEqualPredicate(field='variable', equal= val_type))
    
    line1 = base.mark_trail().encode(
        x = X_name,
        y = Y_name,
        color = "country",
        order = "year",
        #size = "year:O",
        size = alt.Size("year:O", scale = alt.Scale(range = [1,5])),
        opacity = alt.value(0.8),
        #opacity = alt.Opacity("year", scale = alt.Scale(range = [0.2,1])),
    ).transform_filter(
     alt.datum.year <= slider_selection.year
    )

    line2 = base.mark_trail().encode(
        x = X_name,
        y = Y_name,
        #color = "country",
        color = alt.condition(mouse_selection, alt.value("black"), "country"),
        order = "year",
        size = "year:O",
        opacity = alt.value(0.8),
    ).transform_filter(mouse_selection).add_selection(slider_selection).transform_filter(
     alt.datum.year <= slider_selection.year
    )

    circle = base.mark_circle().encode(
        x = X_name,
        y = Y_name,
        color = "country",
        size = alt.value(20),
        #size = alt.Size("year:O", scale = alt.Scale(range = [2,7])),

        tooltip = ["country", "year"],
        #opacity = alt.condition(mouse_selection, alt.value(1), alt.value(1))
    ).add_selection(mouse_selection).transform_filter(
     alt.datum.year <= slider_selection.year).interactive()

    plot = circle + line1 + line2
    
    return plot
